channel.title: Weird Error, help appreciated
channel.description: Hi, I am having an error with my server. I'm not sure if it affects everyone or just locally connecting accounts, but after you log off you apparently cannot log back on. It does not register a connection on the server output and it just gives you the server is down message on the client. Help is appreciated.
